{"tid":1507792,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]白宮聯署被中國黑客入侵","createTime":"2019-08-26T10:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:29:08.000Z","uid":310846,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a0754961d699f6c6b93483a1f00cb340116b6f","tid":1507792,"uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:02:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">白宮聯署數字被凍結  疑與中國黑客入侵有關</span><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮聯署「 We the People 」一向是世界各地人民向美國總統，以政全世界人民表達自己訴求的一個途徑，只要聯署人數能夠在30 天之內到達 100,000 ，美國政府就必須對聯署中談及的議題作出回應。最近社交網路就有人舉出疑似證據，指有來自中國的黑客入侵「 We the People 」網站並對其中一個聯署進行了干擾。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑被黑客「光顧」過的聯署是「 Call for Official recognition of the Chinese Communist Party as a Terrorist Organization. 」，一條關於希望美國政府「正式承認中國共產黨為恐怖組織」的一條聯署。最近有人發現這一條聯署項目疑似被黑客改動過，因為聯署的人數停留了在 87,252 有 18 個小時之多，在 18 個小時間聯署人數一直沒有上升過。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，在 Twitter 上有人宣稱「共軍的黑客把美國白宮的網站給黑了」。該帖子的附圖中亦顯示了「他們」凍結了請願的數據，由「北京時間 2019 年 8 月 25 日 06:51:01 」起將聯署的人數凍結在 87,252 人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/08/26/87252-we-the-people/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2F87252-we-the-people%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=210b03ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/08/26/87252-we-the-people/tech-secure/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/newworldstimes/status/1165661357980684288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewworldstimes%2Fstatus%2F1165661357980684288&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=8177f5ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewworldstimes%2Fstatus%2F1165661357980684288&h=f5937211\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/newworldstimes/status/1165661357980684288</a>"},{"pid":"f56430ae0b015093956f808b4a9bcbb1a97ecd27","tid":1507792,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:02:33.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=40fc73c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY79ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=ebad85f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9f055f7d76ccfc064ee62f4db5620886a81546","tid":1507792,"uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10fc2e42849f45cce4edb545822b8cd4b46434e9","tid":1507792,"uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:03:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b8457c1009c8bbb1bda1fe77bad02d7a22c57ca9","tid":1507792,"uid":310846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d35619b65851f9b38b0d9ecb94399b4ac5bd407","tid":1507792,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506382</a